126
00:09:08,960 --> 00:09:13,210
Yep.. not even once.

127
00:09:14,030 --> 00:09:18,960
Mi Young, you are really too nice, almost to the point that you're an idiot.

128
00:09:21,640 --> 00:09:25,720
You did find it a bit frustrating.

129
00:09:25,720 --> 00:09:31,140
But thanks to you, I went from being 'Post it girl' to 'Bond girl'.

130
00:09:31,140 --> 00:09:34,810
Like the princesses that only appear in movies.

131
00:09:37,080 --> 00:09:41,240
