136
00:09:57,560 --> 00:10:00,870
In the end, you have to make it through on your own.

137
00:10:00,960 --> 00:10:03,710
That's why I'm working hard.

138
00:10:04,850 --> 00:10:09,600
I want to become someone that can give you strength.

139
00:10:09,600 --> 00:10:15,150
So that you'll be able to depend on me,
just as I depended on you.

140
00:10:16,540 --> 00:10:20,870
Just in case your memory returns...

141
00:10:21,910 --> 00:10:27,180
So, if we can be together again...

142
00:10:33,690 --> 00:10:35,700
Your birthday present.

143
