This is what you originally wanted me to make you.

144
00:10:46,410 --> 00:10:48,730
Gunnie cup.

145
00:10:58,470 --> 00:11:02,180
How is it? Looks the same, right?

146
00:11:06,650 --> 00:11:09,240
