147
00:11:10,550 --> 00:11:16,180
Instead, I'll make an upgraded version for next year.

148
00:11:22,960 --> 00:11:25,180
Are you ok?

149
00:11:25,180 --> 00:11:26,940
It has a strong taste.

150
00:11:27,570 --> 00:11:29,250
Here you go.

151
00:11:40,890 --> 00:11:45,350
At first when he found out he was... humiliated like he didn't...

152
