he didn't even really want.. to see his family.

153
00:11:48,180 --> 00:11:53,060
I don't want to give up hope, but seeing him...

154
00:11:53,060 --> 00:11:58,710
changing and looking at my son and knowing that...
It just kind of... hurts.

155
00:11:58,710 --> 00:12:03,300
CEO, these are the files that you have to sign today.

156
00:12:08,800 --> 00:12:12,830
It must be really hard for Madame these days, right?

157
00:12:12,830 --> 00:12:17,730
That's why I brought a plan

158
00:12:17,730 --> 00:12:19,830
