- Secretary Tak.

171
00:13:01,030 --> 00:13:05,110
I think it's my damned genetic disease after all.

172
00:13:05,110 --> 00:13:06,910
So from now, to that nice lady,

173
00:13:06,910 --> 00:13:11,960
I can't even imagine how much pain I will cause her.
I can't even imagine it.

174
00:13:37,920 --> 00:13:42,080
