175
00:13:44,070 --> 00:13:47,930
I was very surprised yesterday because you just left like that.

176
00:13:49,030 --> 00:13:51,710
Se Ra...

177
00:13:53,290 --> 00:13:55,190
Us..

178
00:13:57,450 --> 00:13:59,500
