00:17:56,690 --> 00:18:00,430
Firstly, for the child between Lee Gun and Kim Mi Young,

222
00:18:00,430 --> 00:18:02,880
Kim Mi Young will have

223
00:18:05,010 --> 00:18:07,680
child custody.

224
00:18:07,680 --> 00:18:10,580
Second, after the divorce comes into effect,

225
00:18:10,580 --> 00:18:12,320
Divorce...

226
00:18:12,320 --> 00:18:16,590
Two million dollars will be given to Kim Mi Young as alimony.

