00:44:30,430 --> 00:44:34,950
I have to go to my part-time now. You can spend time here with your mom. I'll see you this evening.

528
00:44:34,950 --> 00:44:37,200
If you want something to eat, call me right away.

529
00:44:37,200 --> 00:44:40,120
Mother, I'm leaving.
- Be careful on your way.

530
00:44:40,120 --> 00:44:42,240
Make yourself at home.

531
00:44:52,100 --> 00:44:53,670
Eat.

532
00:44:53,670 --> 00:44:59,430
Even when the baby is gone, you have to take care of yourself the same as if you had the baby.

533
00:44:59,430 --> 00:45:03,140
Since you had to go through surgery,
I made you seaweed soup only now.

534
00:45:03,140 --> 00:45:07,420
Hurry, and eat. Drink up the broth as well.

535
00:45:14,140 --> 00:45:18,240
You know why I'm not taking you home, right?

536
00:45:18,240 --> 00:45:22,220
If you come home, there will be Mi Ja's son.
Whenever you see the baby,

537
00:45:22,220 --> 00:45:23,650
you'll feel hurt. That's why.

538
00:45:23,650 --> 00:45:25,360
I know.

539
00:45:25,360 --> 00:45:28,920
I know how you feel. Am I a fool?

540
00:45:32,680 --> 00:45:35,230
But then again...

541
00:45:36,290 --> 00:45:40,310
What are you going to do with CEO Lee now?

542
00:45:56,960 --> 00:45:58,090
When did you get here?

543
00:45:58,090 --> 00:46:00,560
Not long ago.

544
00:46:00,560 --> 00:46:02,430
Have a seat.

545
00:46:10,810 --> 00:46:13,390
How is your health?

546
00:46:14,320 --> 00:46:17,260
Are you better?

547
00:46:18,520 --> 00:46:21,920
Why did you lie?

548
00:46:21,920 --> 00:46:26,410
You could have told me that your memory came back.

549
00:46:26,410 --> 00:46:31,650
Was I too much of a burden for you to go that far?

550
00:46:37,530 --> 00:46:40,700
I thought you would feel lighter.

551
00:46:40,700 --> 00:46:44,060
The end was already decided, anyway.

552
00:46:44,060 --> 00:46:47,370
There's no need to get hurt, you know.

553
00:46:49,930 --> 00:46:55,850
For the last time, I want to ask you a foolish question.

554
00:46:57,030 --> 00:46:57,900
Okay.

555
00:46:57,900 --> 00:47:05,150
What if I say, let's forget everything and start over.

556
00:47:05,150 --> 00:47:08,010
It was short but

557
00:47:08,010 --> 00:47:10,410
like before,

558
00:47:12,250 --> 00:47:15,500
can't you stay by my side?

559
00:47:34,730 --> 00:47:37,030
I'm sorry.

560
00:47:38,760 --> 00:47:42,110
Does that answer your question?

561
00:47:42,370 --> 00:47:43,430
Yes.

562
00:47:45,600 --> 00:47:47,980
Definitely.

563
00:47:58,630 --> 00:48:00,790
What is it?

564
00:48:00,790 --> 00:48:03,180
It's our divorce papers.

565
00:48:04,020 --> 00:48:07,270
If I knew it would end like this,

566
00:48:07,270 --> 00:48:11,780
I should have just done it when you wanted me to.

567
00:48:11,780 --> 00:48:15,670
I gave you a big scar.

568
00:48:16,600 --> 00:48:18,070
It's my fault.

569
00:48:18,070 --> 00:48:20,010
No.

570
00:48:20,750 --> 00:48:23,400
It's no one's fault.

571
00:48:25,380 --> 00:48:29,930
We just didn't know that it was a wrong encounter from the beginning.

572
00:49:35,280 --> 00:49:37,650
Baby Diary

573
00:50:39,790 --> 00:50:42,100
I'm sorry.

574
00:51:09,120 --> 00:51:11,450
Wait a moment. Wait.

575
00:51:13,610 --> 00:51:17,160
This is the pickled onion that you made.

576
00:51:17,160 --> 00:51:19,820
They say that the taste of pickled onions change if the owner is gone.

577
00:51:19,820 --> 00:51:21,920
You take it.

578
00:51:24,050 --> 00:51:27,080
Then.. thank you.

579
00:51:27,080 --> 00:51:29,260
I hope the both of you live happily.

580
00:51:29,260 --> 00:51:30,880
Since you keep talking like that,

581
00:51:30,880 --> 00:51:34,380
I remember when I was chased out long time ago.

582
00:51:34,380 --> 00:51:37,920
That's why you should not have only trusted Gun.

583
00:51:37,920 --> 00:51:43,520
Sister-in-law, I'll make sure to beat him up later.

584
00:51:44,720 --> 00:51:47,700
Both of you, please stay healthy.

585
00:51:47,700 --> 00:51:49,400
Goodbye.

586
00:52:14,160 --> 00:52:16,420
When are leaving to go to France?

587
00:52:16,420 --> 00:52:21,040
The day after tomorrow. I'm all packed and now I just have to go.

588
00:52:21,880 --> 00:52:23,420
Yes.

589
00:52:23,820 --> 00:52:25,460
Mi Young.

590
00:52:27,050 --> 00:52:29,280
You're sad that I'm actually about to leave, right?

591
00:52:29,280 --> 00:52:33,590
No matter which neighborhood you live in, it'll be hard to find a neighborhood oppa like me.

592
00:52:51,120 --> 00:52:52,550
What is this?

593
00:52:52,550 --> 00:52:54,490
It's an arts college in Paris.

594
00:52:54,490 --> 00:52:57,860
I think it will be nice if you attend there.

595
00:52:57,860 --> 00:53:01,060
Think about it seriously, for once.

596
00:53:03,130 --> 00:53:05,090
How can I go somewhere like this?

597
00:53:05,090 --> 00:53:07,490
If you put your heart into it, you can do anything.

598
00:53:07,490 --> 00:53:10,710
I'll do whatever I can to help you.

599
00:53:12,540 --> 00:53:14,560
You said this before.

600
00:53:14,560 --> 00:53:18,920
Your life has always been led and ordered around by other people.

601
00:53:18,920 --> 00:53:23,340
If you have courage to change yourself,

602
00:53:23,340 --> 00:53:26,240
it's not bad to just try it

603
00:53:28,450 --> 00:53:31,380
for an new chapter in your life.

604
00:54:51,530 --> 00:54:53,090
Here.

605
00:54:53,090 --> 00:54:56,910
This is the money my son-in-law took from you when he bought the restaurant.

606
00:54:56,910 --> 00:55:00,790
I'm returning this after selling the restaurant.

607
00:55:02,380 --> 00:55:04,200
Mother, this...

608
00:55:05,490 --> 00:55:06,830
It was because I wanted to help with my heart.

609
00:55:06,830 --> 00:55:09,080
It's not only heart...

610
00:55:09,080 --> 00:55:12,930
Even better things... I can't receive anymore, between us.

611
00:55:13,730 --> 00:55:14,930
The rudeness

612
00:55:14,930 --> 00:55:18,750
of my family until now, please forgive it.

613
00:55:20,800 --> 00:55:24,770
With this, you and I...

614
00:55:24,770 --> 00:55:29,380
with no debt to give or receive, we become strangers.

615
00:55:33,520 --> 00:55:35,210
Gun.

616
00:55:36,590 --> 00:55:38,100
Yes.

617
00:55:45,600 --> 00:55:47,870
The way I see it..

618
00:55:47,870 --> 00:55:50,730
You and Mi Young have done all you can.

619
00:55:50,730 --> 00:55:54,680
I don't think it's fate. What can we do?

620
00:55:58,110 --> 00:55:59,850
Mother,

621
00:56:01,130 --> 00:56:03,220
Mi Young...

622
00:56:04,260 --> 00:56:07,500
can I see her just once for the last time?

623
00:56:10,610 --> 00:56:13,260
Our Mi Young

624
00:56:13,260 --> 00:56:15,740
left for abroad today.

625
00:56:17,140 --> 00:56:20,810
I sent her so she can start fresh,

626
00:56:20,810 --> 00:56:24,850
so now you live your life, too.

627
00:56:37,690 --> 00:56:40,780
There was a time when I desired something that can't be done.

628
00:56:40,780 --> 00:56:45,090
♬I must remember you.♬

629
00:56:45,090 --> 00:56:50,580
I would take the jacket you wore to work and hang it on the hook.

630
00:56:50,580 --> 00:56:54,710
While you were resting, I would prepare a delicious dinner.

631
00:56:54,710 --> 00:56:58,400
At the table we would

632
00:56:58,400 --> 00:57:02,110
discuss how the day was and share stories.

633
00:57:02,110 --> 00:57:03,350
Oh, why, why?

634
00:57:03,350 --> 00:57:05,610
While laying my head

635
00:57:05,610 --> 00:57:10,170
on top of your arm, I wanted to be a good wife

636
00:57:10,170 --> 00:57:13,730
who would tell you, "good night".

637
00:57:13,730 --> 00:57:18,590
If you and I were meant for each other,

638
00:57:18,590 --> 00:57:22,440
it would have been nice..

639
00:57:22,440 --> 00:57:28,630
♬Even if parting is sad, even if my heart aches♬

640
00:57:28,630 --> 00:57:32,780
You once said this.
♬If you are happy,♬

641
00:57:32,780 --> 00:57:35,510
If we had met in a better situation,

642
00:57:35,510 --> 00:57:40,870
we would have been destined to be together.

643
00:57:40,900 --> 00:57:44,000
♬As much as I try to erase you♬

644
00:57:44,100 --> 00:57:44,930
Mi Young!

645
00:57:44,940 --> 00:57:47,800
♬ I will miss you♬

646
00:57:47,900 --> 00:57:51,300
♬I will cry ♬

647
00:57:51,310 --> 00:57:52,320
Kim Mi Young!

648
00:57:52,330 --> 00:57:53,720
♬more than today♬

649
00:57:53,820 --> 00:57:57,360
If it hurts this much,
♬Like destiny,♬

650
00:57:57,360 --> 00:58:02,430
then we are not destined to be together.

651
00:58:02,430 --> 00:58:05,970
If we were to ever meet again,

652
00:58:05,970 --> 00:58:17,690
let's pretend not to know each other.

653
00:58:17,690 --> 00:58:21,900
Gun, take care.

654
00:58:23,240 --> 00:58:26,180
Snail!!

655
00:58:27,130 --> 00:58:34,020
♬As much as I erase you, I will miss you more♬

656
00:58:34,020 --> 00:58:40,680
♬More tears will fall than today♬

657
00:58:40,680 --> 00:58:47,260
♬Like destiny, you, who will never come back again,♬

658
00:58:47,260 --> 00:58:54,830
♬You are the only one, only you♬

659
00:58:55,400 --> 00:58:57,860
Three years later

660
00:59:33,380 --> 00:59:37,150
♬ You’re my girl, oh my sunshine ♬

661
00:59:37,150 --> 00:59:40,170
♬ Brighter than sunshine ♬
- CEO!

662
00:59:40,170 --> 00:59:47,340
♬ I wanna feel you I wanna be loved.
Like a dreamy paradise ♬

663
00:59:47,340 --> 00:59:54,520
Daniel!
- You came?
♬ A love story like the movies, since we met like destiny ♬

664
00:59:54,520 --> 01:00:03,780
♬ I’m nervous, my heart races.
Like I have been enchanted, I’m falling in love ♬

665
01:00:03,780 --> 01:00:10,500
♬ I look for you like a habit. I think of you like a routine ♬

666
01:00:10,500 --> 01:00:14,500
♬ My clueless heart must have not realized that it is love♬
